{
  "nodes": [
    {"id":"aTitle","type":"text","x":-40,"y":-180,"width":900,"height":120,"text":"# Jarvis — Current Architecture\n\nTwo processes over one WebSocket. Hardware-bound work on **Windows**; **LLM + memory** in WSL."},
    {"id":"aLegend","type":"text","x":900,"y":-180,"width":740,"height":120,"text":"**Legend** — 🟦 Windows · 🟪 WSL core · 🟩 memory/data · 🟧 external service.\nBoundary = WebSocket `:8765`. Red edge = wired-incorrectly (see status)."},
    {"id":"aRepo","type":"link","x":1680,"y":-180,"width":300,"height":120,"url":"https://github.com/jmtitan/Jarvis"},

    {"id":"gWin","type":"group","x":-40,"y":-20,"width":960,"height":760,"label":"Windows Desktop — D:\\Jarvis\\src","color":"5"},
    {"id":"gWsl","type":"group","x":1120,"y":-20,"width":960,"height":760,"label":"WSL Core — ~/workspace/Jarvis/core","color":"6"},
    {"id":"gExt","type":"group","x":300,"y":800,"width":1500,"height":210,"label":"External services / binaries"},

    {"id":"a_main","type":"text","x":0,"y":20,"width":880,"height":120,"color":"5","text":"**JarvisAssistant** `main.py`\nbg asyncio thread + queues · wake-word / continuous · interruption · orchestration"},
    {"id":"a_listen","type":"text","x":0,"y":170,"width":280,"height":100,"color":"5","text":"**AudioListener** `audio/listener.py`\nmic + WebRTC VAD"},
    {"id":"a_stt","type":"text","x":300,"y":170,"width":280,"height":100,"color":"5","text":"**WhisperSTT** `stt/whisper_stt.py`\nspeech → text"},
    {"id":"a_tts","type":"text","x":600,"y":170,"width":280,"height":100,"color":"5","text":"**VoiceSynthesizer** `tts/voice_synthesizer.py`\nEdge TTS"},
    {"id":"a_play","type":"text","x":0,"y":300,"width":280,"height":100,"color":"5","text":"**Playback** `_play_audio` (pygame)\ninterruptible (50ms poll)"},
    {"id":"a_ui","type":"text","x":300,"y":300,"width":280,"height":100,"color":"5","text":"**UI** `ui_manager.py`\ntray · settings · hotkeys"},
    {"id":"a_cc","type":"text","x":600,"y":300,"width":280,"height":120,"color":"5","text":"**CoreClient** `core_client.py`\nWebSocket client (request/reply by id)"},
    {"id":"a_cfgw","type":"text","x":0,"y":450,"width":280,"height":90,"color":"5","text":"**config.yaml** (Windows)\naudio · stt · tts · hotkeys · core host"},

    {"id":"a_srv","type":"text","x":1160,"y":20,"width":880,"height":110,"color":"6","text":"**WS endpoint** `core/server.py` — bind `0.0.0.0:8765`\nroutes chat · interrupt · stats"},
    {"id":"a_chat","type":"text","x":1160,"y":150,"width":880,"height":90,"color":"6","text":"**chat_service.py**\nbuild prompt → generate → persist"},
    {"id":"a_oll","type":"text","x":1160,"y":270,"width":420,"height":110,"color":"2","text":"**OllamaClient** `llm/ollama_client.py`\n→ Ollama (llama3)"},
    {"id":"a_mm","type":"text","x":1600,"y":270,"width":440,"height":110,"color":"4","text":"**MemoryManager** `memory/memory_manager.py`\nbuild_enhanced_prompt · process_interaction"},
    {"id":"a_persona","type":"text","x":1160,"y":400,"width":420,"height":110,"color":"1","text":"**Persona** `prompts/Emma.md`\nsystem prompt — ⚠️ orphaned (see status.canvas)"},
    {"id":"a_pb","type":"text","x":1600,"y":400,"width":210,"height":110,"color":"4","text":"**PromptBuilder**\n6-section prompt\n(hardcoded system)"},
    {"id":"a_vs","type":"text","x":1830,"y":400,"width":210,"height":110,"color":"4","text":"**VectorStore**\nsimilarity search"},
    {"id":"a_cfgc","type":"text","x":1160,"y":530,"width":420,"height":90,"color":"6","text":"**config.yaml** (core)\nollama · memory · core bind"},
    {"id":"a_data","type":"text","x":1600,"y":530,"width":440,"height":110,"color":"4","text":"**memory_data/**\nuser_profile · conversation · long_term · entries · `vectors.npy` (JSON + npy)"},

    {"id":"a_whisper","type":"text","x":320,"y":840,"width":420,"height":120,"color":"2","text":"**whisper.cpp**\n`whisper_bin/` + `models/` (tiny/base.en)"},
    {"id":"a_edge","type":"text","x":760,"y":840,"width":420,"height":120,"color":"2","text":"**Edge TTS** (cloud)\nneeds internet"},
    {"id":"a_ollama_ext","type":"text","x":1200,"y":840,"width":420,"height":120,"color":"2","text":"**Ollama** (WSL, GPU)\nHTTP `:11434` · model llama3"}
